reviewText: love these DVD'S by Karyn Henley they are great.

Karyn Henley has done it again.  My granddaughter loves these Christian tapes.
My grandson who is now eighteen watched "Five Little Ladybugs" continuously when he was a toddler. These tapes appeal to little ones.
We have always enjoyed Karyn's videos and this qas a delight as well. My kids interact with her as she interacts with the kids on the video. The kitchen band has started in our home now! :-)

Bought this as replacement for VHS tape at our church. Henley reaches to the child's spirit & soul through delightful music. I'm looking forward to a new generation of kids enjoying this particular collection.
We love all of Karyn Henley's resources that we have so far.  Great messages, really appreciate the biblical and moral values presented.

We've had "Feel Like A Giggle" for a year and the kids l-o-v-e it!  Karen engages them and keeps them transfixed and singing along on 'Noah's," too.  This DVD is more overtly Sunday schoolish and doesn't intersperse the overtly Christian themes as sparsely as does "Giggle."  We love having new songs to learn and dance to and will likely be getting her "Ladybug" DVD soon!  Highly recommended.
